{"tid":653476,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小心呢間嘢啲食物","createTime":"2018-05-04T18:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T18:09:35.000Z","uid":184606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0965bd3e5a0f039ff5371ed49a99272570a6b6ab","tid":653476,"uid":184606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T18:09:35.000Z","msg":"我有朋友於4月中係Season Plus 食完生蠔後痾嘔，其後傳染了家人，小朋友痾嘔到有脫水徵狀要入院，之後驗到中左諾如病毒Norovirus GI/GII。一種傳染性極高的貝殻類病毒，係食物中毒既一種，之後小朋友要留醫同隔離。不過小朋友係當中係冇接觸過海鮮既。<br />\n<br />\n因事件嚴重，現已轉介至衛生署及食環署跟進，衛生署回覆仍在調查及收集數據中，現呼籲如市民曾於上述餐廳進食生蠔而又出現痾嘔症狀請馬上聯絡衛生署或政府熱線：1823。<br />\n<br />\n由於諾如病毒傳染性極高，很容易於社區、學校及人多地方爆發，具24-48小時潛服期，大部分患者一般三日可以改善，唯兒童、長者及抵抗力差人士會有脫水及死亡風險。以下連結有更多資料。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160119/19457671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160119%2F19457671&d=LiGpq4PHcy29c2DU02GkF1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=cbfe8ce2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160119%2F19457671&h=d9c452dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160119/19457671</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/healthtopics/content/24/33.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chp.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fhealthtopics%2Fcontent%2F24%2F33.html&d=LiGpq4PHcy29c2DU02GkF1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=58cf3408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chp.gov.hk/tc/healthtopics/content/24/33.html</a>"}]}